{"tid":661281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：大灣區涉及三地政府　不能以香港利益為先","createTime":"2018-05-11T12:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T06:05:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1f4e4292d2fe911d341a88eb047207dd203f65","tid":661281,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"港澳辦主任張曉明在成都，出席川港高層會晤時表示，中央領導對粵港澳大灣區和港珠澳大橋等，內地與港澳合作項目作出指示，包括要充分尊重特區政府的意見。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥說，已往有很多機會與中央政府、港澳辦和中聯辦合作，中央從來尊重香港，特區政府官員作為管治香港第一責任人，儘管很多問題初期有不同看法，但中央最終尊重香港意見，張曉明只是重申一向的原則。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，大灣區涉及三地政府，更加需要互相尊重，不能以香港看法或利益為先，強調工作原則是互補、互惠共贏。她又說，每項基建發展都作出評估，自己最不願意看到香港停滯不前，目前也看不到有任何基建是「無用」。"},{"pid":"49e319fcd876748002f8985a4b0bc8470ebc8803","tid":661281,"uid":107212,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"呢啲咩邏輯黎<br />\n<br />\n一個地方嘅首長竟然唔係以自己地方利益為先<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係賣港賊"},{"pid":"75096b6dcd1f08d526fec1c68347cf68cfa3d1ec","tid":661281,"uid":27664,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"正宗賣港婦"},{"pid":"b4266864204b31e208edcbbabffaab3dec7092c2","tid":661281,"uid":40763,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<br />\n香港人其實可以忍到點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ce93fd0c73bc34cd2c3084311e79b29efc8685","tid":661281,"uid":57023,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"49e319fcd876748002f8985a4b0bc8470ebc8803","tid":661281,"uid":107212,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"呢啲咩邏輯黎<br />\n<br />\n一個地方嘅首長竟然唔係以自己地方利益為先<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係賣港賊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:30:10.000Z","msg":"一早就知佢責任不嬲唔係為HK人爭取利益，但佢任務一定盡力出賣HK人最多利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b9bad5a41a08313f262883b2b1c178704eccfd","tid":661281,"uid":41500,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"如果而家落搭既香港後生唔夠多,咪比我睇中遲早一定夾硬足夠數過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論係一賄一賂、大鳩區、同水左香港人好耐既所謂北上發展<br />\n根本就係港版楢山節考、デンデラ野<br />\n<br />\n唯一分別,係日版因為貧困老人丟棄自己,資源留比後生<br />\n港版係老果代就明明物質豐裕,都仲要推年輕一代落火坑,黎滿足佢地收尾幾年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地又好意思話一代不如一代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錯呀佢地就真係不如日本果代啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1a77823ca42d1aa0cdd64aabd4b61d40c67631","tid":661281,"uid":119347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"作為香港嘅管治者竟然可以講得出呢啲噉嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab3967902d04177c6f2d87c4caddde63b2a1d68","tid":661281,"uid":57023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dd1a77823ca42d1aa0cdd64aabd4b61d40c67631","tid":661281,"uid":119347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"作為香港嘅管治者竟然可以講得出呢啲噉嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"佢係真正管治者嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢只係個傀儡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c1c7db0a183f5c90a925b77390ad190c5f5bf0","tid":661281,"uid":25952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"都唔見得香港政府係香港政策上會以港人利益為先啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409eab7ecc63a1aa0859fb82ff455c2eb37ee087","tid":661281,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05